dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T23:25:13.000Z","msg":"試下戒牛奶、奶製品同甜野，之後每日飲起碼2L水<br />\n<br />\n洗面我自己用Physiogel,Cetaphil,Papulex 個啲，萬寧屈臣氏有售"},{"pid":"8007f85b51a4d5a42798bf04a1f43354fca0a78e","tid":120791,"uid":19301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T23:31:10.000Z","msg":"可能係空氣問題"},{"pid":"5b051417a8f67b7cc3f9e72a17853e1831eaca24","tid":120791,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T23:45:54.000Z","msg":"睇醫生食a酸啦"},{"pid":"350556620a999c9f5709ca9b7d0111446b964886","tid":120791,"uid":41735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T23:58:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個腮位好多暗瘡 懷疑係身體出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以去睇中醫調理下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5d5cc1b348c9ab813bc3b6b0e58feb4339e4e5","tid":120791,"uid":42343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T00:14:39.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你試晒上面果d 所謂建議都要幾個月，到時唔得又整多幾個凹凸洞，要唔知幾多次laser 先醫到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081184f51190273000db7f01ff682b28ccba9cb9","tid":120791,"uid":29863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T01:33:10.000Z","msg":"腮位好多暗粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0adb29387dbebf4a74ed5c35edf64156311d85","tid":120791,"uid":62722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T01:34:49.000Z","msg":"晚晚十點訓半年都唔好先講啦"},{"pid":"88c8cff11a1023aae0efda816b3cf04fe2e2894d","tid":120791,"uid":656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T01:39:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得乜都唔查係最好  一查左塊面就會好油好笠  唔查反而乾爽勁少油  (生暗瘡係因為多面油)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你又知唔知塊面乾先會出面油</blockquote><br />\n呢個絕對唔係直接嘅因果關係<br />\n唔好誤導人<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/16/093853_88c1f8ac2a32f0f4825a9b86343a9a04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F16%2F093853_88c1f8ac2a32f0f4825a9b86343a9a04.jpg&h=afdcad3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39543cd412e9059b676d5503e8109700aec8f550","tid":120791,"uid":656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T01:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打多謝你咁詳細答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泰國隻黑頭貼上網都見好多review, 效果幾好不過始終唔想用d拉扯性咁強既產品，始終我個鼻毛孔都開始大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打嘅講法我不敢苟同，首先kielhs 本身啲野就係垃圾，又多色素又唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其次就係佢係loreal group,更加唔值得買<br />\n<br />\n另外爽膚水，精華，cream唔係must<br />\n爽膚水係等你皮膚更好吸收之後product,我推介花水<br />\n扺用嘅有florihana<br />\n天然extract 無防腐劑 唔貴 一定好過萬寧買到嘅爽膚水<br />\n暗瘡問題應該可以用永久花/橙花<br />\n<br />\n油肌cream嘅質地就太厚重啦<br />\n我見過有油肌朋友連精華都嫌笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愈水，啲分子愈細愈好<br />\n油肌查精華就夠啦<br />\n<br />\n去角質可以好多方式嘅deep clean,<br />\n比較好嘅有paula's choice 嘅bha,同埋去永興買高岭土泥<br />\n唔算貴，有效去角質<br />\n黑頭真係香港一日咁污糟都唔會解決到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擦子膠去角質只係令你感覺良好，事實係你捽果陣將佢入面啲成份組合過先出擦子膠碎，令你覺得好似捽左角質出黎<br />\n其實係無鬼用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}